euse, qui désirent mieux comprendre les procédures formelles de la raison ou qui veulent, par curiosité, augmenter leur connaissance de l’histoire fascinante des idées en Occident.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 7aPHILOSOPHY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311127365508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2017z978311127619940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978276373145240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763731452423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763731452/original  a978-3-11-127365-5  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  a978-3-11-127619-9  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2017b2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles